<article>
    <h1>Bread Street Kitchen&#x2019;s Na&#xAD;tional Burger Week Specials</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200821/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-08-21"><time>2020-08-21</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE | HAPPENINGS</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>The restau­rant has in­tro­duced three burger specials for a lim­ited pe­riod: pulled pork burger; soft-shell crab burger with a whole crispy soft-shell crab blan­keted in chilli crab may­on­naise; and lamb burger, a spiced lamb mer­guez patty ac­com­pa­nied with smoked feta cheese, tzatziki sauce and mar­i­nated cu­cum­ber be­tween slices of a re­fresh­ing mint brioche. Din­ers can opt for the burger slider sam­pler ($56++) to en­joy all three burg­ers.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Bread Street Kitchen by Gor­don Ram­say, L1-81 Bay Level,</p>
    <p>The Shoppes at Ma­rina Bay Sands, 2 Bayfront Av­enue MRT: Bayfront</p>
    <p>WHEN: 11.30am - 10pm (Mon - Wed), 11.30am - 11pm (Thu & Fri), 8.30am - 11pm (Sat) & 8.30am - 10pm (Sun)</p>
    <p>TEL: 6688-5665 INFO: www.ma­rina baysands.com/restau­rants/ bread-street-kitchen.html</p>


